    "title": "Loan Origination Under Strain",
    "description": "Your bank's Loan Origination Service processes every application synchronously: a fragile Core Banking Adapter, a slow external credit bureau, and a customer database without connection pooling. Approvals crawl, the adapter keeps timing out under load, and there's barely enough capacity to keep up. There are far more possible fixes than budget for - pick wisely.",
    "difficulty": "advanced",
    "tags": [
      "caching",
      "async-messaging",
      "horizontal-scaling",
      "vertical-scaling",
      "legacy-integration",
      "cost-optimization"
    ],
    "estimatedMinutes": 30
  },
